Officer Michael Slager , 33 , is charged with murder after opening fire on Walter Scott , 50 , after stopping him over a broken tail light in North Charleston , South Carolina , on Saturday .
His attorney Andy Savage told Slager is housed in a room with one small window and does not have any interaction with any other detainees at Charleston County jail .
Slager 's mother is expected to visit her son Friday for the first time since the shooting .